OL,4,Creveal extent of violence against NHS
OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FThere are calls for a zero tolerance
OL,8,Fapproach to aggression against health
OL,9,Fworkers after new figures were
OL,10,Frevealed showing the scale of
OL,11,Fincidents against NHS staff in
OL,12,FLancashire.
OL,14,FA report to a meeting of the Blackpool
OL,15,FTeaching Hospitals board of directors
OL,16,Fsaid 456 incidents of violence were
OL,17,Freported during 2023/24, including
OL,18,Fboth physical attacks (279) and verbal
OL,19,Fassaults (177).
