OL,7,FHe asked for further reports on the
OL,8,Fissue so the board could help the
OL,9,FTrust deal with the problem.
OL,11,FAngela Parfitt, deputy director of
OL,12,Fquality governance at Blackpool
OL,13,FTeaching Hospitals, said it had been
OL,14,Fnationally recognised that there had
OL,15,Fbeen an increase "in terms of violence
OL,16,Fand aggression within the NHS."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
