OL,7,FShe said, "For us we have a more
OL,8,Fchallenging demographic so we are
OL,9,Fhigher but that is reflective of that,
OL,10,Fso we have to keep that balance in
OL,11,Fcontext."
OL,13,FShe added that the Trust's health and
OL,14,Fsafety committee was carrying out work
OL,15,Faround sanctions to ensure there was
OL,16,Fconsistency around that.
