OL,7,FTraining had also been offered to
OL,8,Fstaff in how best to handle violence
OL,9,Fand aggression which the report said
OL,10,Fhad "improved staff confidence in
OL,11,Fconflict resolution techniques" and
OL,12,Fwas "reducing the risk to staff of
OL,13,Fverbal and physical assault."
OL,15,FThe Trust operates Blackpool Victoria
OL,16,FHospital, known locally as The Vic,
OL,17,Fwhich serves people living in and
OL,18,Fvisiting Blackpool, Fylde and Wyre.
