OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FA national NHS Staff Survey carried
OL,8,Fout in 2023 found nearly 14 per cent
OL,9,Fof staff who took part said they had
OL,10,Fexperienced at least one incident of
OL,11,Fphysical violence from patients,
OL,12,Fservice users, relatives or other
OL,13,Fmembers of the public in the previous
OL,14,F12 months.
OL,16,FRecent national reports have also
OL,17,Frevealed at least 55 ambulance staff
OL,18,Fare abused or attacked every day
OL,19,Facross the country, according to the
OL,20,FAssociation of Ambulance Chief
OL,21,FExecutives.
